title: Ben Yuan Vegetarian
description: 本愿素食 is a veg stall inside Li Soon Coffee shop.  Offers white/brown rice or bee hoon/noodles, and eat it with dishes like broccoli, cauliflower, kailan, brinjal, curry. At dinner time tze char dishes like yang zhou fried rice, fried hokkien noodle. No garlic, onion, or egg. Closes alternate Tuesday except if it falls 1st or 15th day of lunar month.
